<html>
    <head>
        <title>Confirm Account</title>
    </head>
    <body style="background-image: linear-gradient(187.16deg, #181623 0.07%, #191725 51.65%, #0D0B14 98.75%);">
        <div style="padding-left: 5%; padding-right: 5%; padding-top: 6%; color: #ffffff;">
            <p style="color: #DDCCAA; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; margin-top: 10px;">Product Page</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 72px;">Hola {{name}}!</p>
            <p>Thanks for joining Movie quotes! We really appreciate it. Please click the button below to verify your account:</p>
            <button style="width: 128px; height:38px; background-color: #E31221; border-radius: 4px; border:none;">
                <a href="{{link}}" style="text-decoration: none; color: #ffffff;">Verify account</a>
            </button>
            <p>If clicking doesn't work, you can try copying and pasting it to your browser:</p>
            <p style="word-break: break-word; color: #DDCCAA;">{{link}}</p>
            <p style="padding-bottom: 100px;">Product Page</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>